quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  26,84,"Go Sunggai yakongka sa Bantogan a mapiya si-i ko phanga­ o ori"
  26,85,"Go Baloya Kongka a pud ko manga waris ko Sorga a Pakalma;"
  26,86,"Go Napi-i ngka si Ama, Mata-an! A sukaniyan na miyabaloi a pud ko Miyangadadadag;"
  26,87,"Go Diyakongka Phakaron­ dana ko gawi-i a Kaoyaga kiran (ko Alongan a Qiyamah);-"
  26,88,"Gawi-i a di phakanggai a gona so Tamok, go so manga Wata,"
  26,89,"Inonta so tao a minitalingo­ ma Niyan ko Allah so poso a Li­nang;"
  26,90,"Na ipakarani so Sorga ko Miyamananggila,"
  26,91,"Go Pakisandungan so Nar­aka Jahim ko Miyangadadadag;"
  26,92,"Go Tharo-on kiran: Anda so sukano na Pushimba-an niyo,-"
  26,93,"A salakao ko Allah? Ino khatabangan kano iran, o di na khatabangan niran a ginawa iran?"
  26,94,"Na Panalimpato-on siran ro­o siran a go so Miyangadadadag,"
  26,95,"Go so pagtao o lblis sa kasamasama iran."
  26,96,"Tharo-on niran a siran na gi­ i siran ro-o shasawala:"
  26,97,"lbut ko Allah, ka Mata-an a miyatago kami dun ko kadadag a mapayag,"
  26,98,"Gowani a irimbang ami su­ kano ko Kadnan o manga Ka-adun;"
  26,99,"Na da-a miyakadadag ruka­mi a rowar ko manga rarata i ongar."
  26,100,"Na da-a bagiyan nami a phamakaogop,"
  26,101,"Go da-a bolayoka a goma­gut sa ginawa (ko masosowa ami)."
  26,102,"Na o Mata-an! A adun a kapakakasoi ami (sa doniya), na mabaloi kami a pud ko Miyamara­ tiyaya!"
  26,103,"Mata-an! A adun a matata­go roo man a titho a Tanda, na da mabaloi so kadakulan kiran a Khi­paparatiyaya."
  26,104,"Na Mata-an! A so Kadnan Ka na Sukaniyan ndun so Maba­gur, a Makalimo-on."
  26,105,"Piyakambokhag o pagtao o Nuh so manga Sogo."
  26,106,"Gowani na Pitharo kiran o Pagari ran a Nuh: Ino kano di Phananggila?"
  26,107,"Mata-an! A Sakun na Sogo rukano a kasasana-an:"
  26,108,"Na kalukun niyo so Allah, go Onoti Yako niyo."
  26,109,"Na da-a Phangunin Ko rukano saya a balas: Da-a balas Rakun inonta si-i ko Kadnan o manga Ka-adun:"
  26,110,"Na kalukun niyo so Allah, go Onoti Ako niyo."
  26,111,"Pitharo iran: Ino ami Suka Pharatiyaya-a a aya Phagonot Ruka na so tanto a manga bababa?"